                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hay</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hunter</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1899-07-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 22, 1899</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Hay directs that correspondence in the Pears case be transmitted to the
                    Department, and that Mr. Hunter await instructions.)</p>
